(64549, -1, 'email_start_text', 'cphelptext', 'On this screen you select criteria to determine who your email is sent to. These criteria are described below.<br /><br />\r\nKeep in mind all criteria are cumulative; that is, if you enter a username string to match and select a usergroup, users that match the username string AND are in the selected group will be found, but those that match only one of the above will not.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
