(65629, -1, 'options_options_softlinebreakchars_text', 'cphelptext', 'The option is related to the permission that controls how many lines a user may have in his or her signature.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA line of text without a hard linebreak may wrap when displayed in a browser and actually appear as two lines. This option controls how many characters (other than linebreaks) that are allowed before the text counts as multiple lines.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1155818656, '3.6.1', 0),
