(65633, -1, 'options_options_allowsmilies_text', 'cphelptext', 'If you enable this setting, users can type such text as :) and :( and they will be converted into smilie images in non forum specific areas. Otherwise, the text will be displayed as text.\r\nThis setting is not used anywhere in vBulletin itself, but may be used by addons/plugins.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1172666320, '3.6.5', 0),
