(65643, -1, 'options_options_avatarenabled_text', 'cphelptext', 'If you enable this setting, users will able to choose avatars, small pictures which show up on their posts under their usernames. You can enable/disable avatars on a per-usergroup level by disabling their ability to use any avatar categories under Avatars > Avatar Manager. You can enable/disable custom avatars in Usergroups > Usergroup Manager.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
