(65651, -1, 'options_options_reputationundefined_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the reputation ''description'' that will be given to any user that has a reputation that is lesser than the smallest reputation level.<br /><br />For example, if your lowest reputation is -300, any user with a reputation of -301 or smaller will have this description.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
