(65653, -1, 'options_options_reputationdefault_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the reputation level that each user is given when they register. You as the administrator must have a level that is at least equal to or less than this value.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nIf you change this value then you may want to <a href="misc.php?do=chooser" target="_blank">rebuild your reputations</a> to give existing users to same base reputation level.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
