(65683, -1, 'options_options_enablememberlist_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is enabled, the display of the Member List will be enabled. The Member List shows all users who are in groups that have "Viewable on Memberlist" enabled in Usergroups.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
