(66489, -1, 'thread_move_text', 'cphelptext', 'This page allows you to mass move threads based on several criterion.  Fill in the options below and click the "Move Threads" button to proceed.  Clicking the "Move Threads" button will not perform the moving, but will instead give you the option to move all matching threads or to selectively move.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
