(65859, -1, 'options_options_maxmultipage_text', 'cphelptext', 'If a thread has 75 pages you probably don''t want a link to each page in the forum''s thread listing page.  Use this option to limit the number of linked pages.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
