(64399, -1, 'css_doedit_text', 'cphelptext', 'On this screen you can edit a large number of style options relating to your forums display. Each style can have its'' own set of CSS and images by customizing the items on this screen.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
