(64403, -1, 'css_doedit_headinclude_text', 'cphelptext', 'The contents of the headinclude template are inserted within the &lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt; tags on each forum page.  Meta tags, style sheets, scripts, etc are added here.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
