(64431, -1, 'css_doedit_imgdir_button_text', 'cphelptext', 'The button images folder contains images like the "New Thread" and "Post Reply" images.  Because these images contain language-specific text you can override this setting in the language manager.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nEnter a directory path that is relative to your forum directory (e.g., <b>images/buttons</b>).', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
