(64435, -1, 'css_doedit_imgdir_attach_text', 'cphelptext', 'Attachment icons are used to identify different types of attached files.  The names of these images use the file type they are representing.  For example, the image for zip files is named zip.gif and is uploaded to the attachment icon folder.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nEnter a directory path that is relative to your forum directory (e.g., <b>images/attach</b>).', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
