(64437, -1, 'css_doedit_imgdir_misc_text', 'cphelptext', 'The miscellaneous images folder contains miscellaneous images.  Examples include the instant messenger icons and the vb_bullet.gif icon.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nEnter a directory path that is relative to your forum directory (e.g., <b>images/misc</b>).', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1148680118, '3.6.0 Beta 1', 0),
