(64439, -1, 'css_doedit_imgdir_editor_text', 'cphelptext', 'The text editor controls folder contains the small shortcut images used in the vBulletin text editors (like the WYSIWYG text editor).<br /><br />\r\n\r\nEnter a directory path that is relative to your forum directory (e.g., <b>images/editor</b>).', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
