(64447, -1, 'css_doedit_imgdir_reputation_text', 'cphelptext', 'The reputation images folder contains the little colored dot images that are used to display a user''s reputation.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nEnter a directory path that is relative to your forum directory (e.g., <b>images/reputation</b>).', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
