(65269, -1, 'options_options_pmthrottleperiod_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the period of time of which throttle checking is performed.  The amount of messages that a user can send within this period is defined by their Message Throttle Quantity usergroup permission.  If this is set to 0 then private messages will not be throttled.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1220958342, '3.8.0 Alpha 1', 0),
