(64601, -1, 'forum_add_edit_daysprune_text', 'cphelptext', 'This determines how many days worth of threads are shown on forumdisplay. The value chosen here will be used by guests as well as forum members that leave this option set to "Forum Default" in their settings. Users can also change this temporarily by using the controls at the bottom of forumdisplay.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
