(64603, -1, 'forum_add_edit_defaultsortfield_text', 'cphelptext', 'This controls the field that threads are sorted using by default. Users may still selectively override this setting and resort using the controls at the bottom of the thread list.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote that to select sorting by thread rating, ratings must be enabled for this forum. If they are not, the forum will be sorted by last post.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1142519066, '3.6.0 Beta 1', 0),
