(64625, -1, 'forum_add_edit_password_text', 'cphelptext', 'If you set a password, a user will be required to enter that password before being allowed to enter this forum. The user must have cookies turned on to enter a password-protected forum. This password will be inherited by subforums unless those subforums have Can Have Password set to No. If a user knows the password but is in a usergroup that is not allowed to access that forum, the user will <i>not</i> be allowed to access it.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
