(64635, -1, 'forum_add_edit_indexposts_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to No, posts made in this forum from this point on will <i>not</i> be indexed by the search engine. Such posts will not able to be searched for. This is desirable if you have a "Testing" type forum, or a forum that is chit-chat that you don''t want indexed.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 0, '', 0),
